    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Notice on Headset Compatibility </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Now with Valve Index Support! </strong></li></ul><br>Please note that Hello Neighbor VR has been tested on, and currently fully supports, the following devices:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Meta Quest 2, Meta Quest Pro<br></li><li> Oculus Rift S<br></li><li> Valve Index</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Hello Neighbor VR!</h2><strong>《Hello Neighbor: Search and Rescue》</strong>是一款极具开创性的VR恐怖解谜游戏。在这款游戏里，你需要潜入古怪的邻居家中，解救自己的朋友。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206320/extras/b339b4d82c9dc4d2e736fb4998388c44.poster.avif?t=1728835378\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206320/extras/b339b4d82c9dc4d2e736fb4998388c44.webm?t=1728835378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206320/extras/b339b4d82c9dc4d2e736fb4998388c44.mp4?t=1728835378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>多个可扮演的角色：</strong>在多个角色之间切换，智胜邻居。每个独特角色都有自己的关键道具和技能。在尝试进入恐怖地下室的过程中，自由切换救援队成员的视角，破解谜题并躲避邻居！<br> <br></li><li><strong>随环境而变的谜题需要创造性的解决方法：</strong>你将不得不越发绞尽脑汁，寻找各种替代方案来克服一系列动态谜题，以及充满挑战的随环境而变的障碍。许多谜题乍看之下似乎不可能破解，你需要结合运用多个角色的视角才能化解它们。<br> <br></li><li><strong>非线性探索：</strong>运用你自己的方式潜入皮特森先生的房子。你可以改换视角、组合角色技能，以便动态破解谜题、揭开隐藏的秘密和发现新路径来突破所处环境。<br> <br></li><li><strong>直面你的恐惧</strong>：随着救援小队更深入地了解《Hello Neighbor》宇宙的秘密，体验超现实且令人不安的启示！</li></ul>",
